### 解题思路
先排序再遍历

时间复杂度O(nlog(n))
空间复杂度O(1)

### 代码

```python3
class Solution:
    def maximumGap(self, nums: List[int]) -> int:
        if len(nums)<2: return 0
        nums.sort()
        res = nums[1]-nums[0]
        for i in range(2,len(nums)):
            res = max(nums[i]-nums[i-1],res)
        return res
```
